[D7]We had no phone and the doctor lived too [G]far
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[C]I said momma I reckon I'd best go fetch the [G]neighbor
[D7]She said I'll be all right there ain't no [G]need
[C]But she kept on gettin' worse instead of [G]better
[D7]With a feverish look she pleaded up at [G]me
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[C]She said son run to the spring and get some [G]water
